Since our work commenced, we have been needing to transport large amounts of supplies to Zirgorteh the Open-armed.
While we have simple, sturdy carts for this purpose, there is presently not enough to meet demand. I wish to build more, and ask that you furnish us with some necessary parts.
<Split(<Highlight>ObjectParameter(1)</Highlight>, ,1)/>, might I trouble you to furnish us with cart components again?
The conveyances assembled using your parts are highly favored for their maneuverability, and I have a mind to build more.
Garharlor yonder has the materials you require, so please present yourself to him. My thanks in advance.
You are helping us build carts? Good, good, quality components are always welcome.
Without further ado, then, please use these materials to prepare parts for the underframe. If you run out, I shall provide you with more.
Without further ado, then, please use these materials to prepare parts for the dampener. If you run out, I shall provide you with more.
Without further ado, then, please use these materials to prepare parts for the axle. If you run out, I shall provide you with more.
When the items are ready, you may deliver them directly to Vuyargur. I wish you happy crafting.
Do you require more materials? You need but say the word if so.
To be deleted.
To be deleted.
You require more materials? Here, please use these.
To be deleted.
To be deleted.
Ah, <Split(<Highlight>ObjectParameter(1)</Highlight>, ,1)/>. How are the cart components coming along?
Sturdy <Emphasis>and</Emphasis> light... At scarcely more than a glance, you were able to identify a point for improvement. You truly are an extraordinary artisan.
You spare no effort, and it shows in the finish. I receive these with thanks.
We Yok Huy traditionally build with stone and wood, and typically prioritize strength at the cost of weight.

Given the mountainous terrain in which the carts will be used, however, it would be wise to keep weight to a limit. Your components help us to achieve that, and I shall enjoy assembling the final product with them.
